vote.title: Authorize the Fifth Amendment to the contract for the Dallas Museum of Art located at 1717 North Harwood Street, to extend the term of the contract from May 1, 2023 to May 1, 2025 - Financing: This action has no cost consideration to the City (see Fiscal Information)
